                        <interp inst="t18431127-name-490" type="surname" value="ROBERTS"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18431127-name-490" type="given" value="BENJAMIN"></interp>BENJAMIN ROBERTS</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-sergeant.</hi>) On the 17th of Nov., I was called and took the prisoner in Mr. Luff's shop—I asked how he came by the diamond—he said it was given him by a young man named Farmer, and if I took him outside he would point him out.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> I met Samuel Farmer as I was going to market; he and he had picked it up; I was a good while before I would take it.</p>
